{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530280/extras/Logo_Steam.png?t=1728937720\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Blooming</strong> is a <strong>2D platformer action game</strong> with a pixel art/retro style. You play as Rose, a student at Bastion wizardry academy; which has been invaded by a monster army send by non other than your own god.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You must explore different areas of the school, every one of them with a unique theme based on elements. Defeat each zone\u00b4s boss in any order you want, for you to gain their power and confront <strong>\u201cThe Heavenly Creator\u201d</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Side scrolling platforming</strong> and action. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530280/extras/F1.gif?t=1728937720\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Combat inspired by classics:</strong> you have a bow that can be turned into dual blades. Attack either at close distance or range. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530280/extras/F2.gif?t=1728937720\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Elemental arrows system:</strong> by defeating bosses you can unlock their powers in the form of an elemental arrow. You can change your active arrow at any moment. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530280/extras/F3.gif?t=1728937720\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bosses and areas can be explored in any order</strong>,  but maybe you can use one element to defeat another\u2026 <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530280/extras/F4.gif?t=1728937720\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Find and defeat optional bosses:</strong> these bosses will upgrade the arrow from the boss of their specific zone. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530280/extras/F5.gif?t=1728937720\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You can jump and use a dash</strong>, use these tools to fight and move around levels efficiently. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530280/extras/F6.gif?t=1728937720\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Need healing or ammo?:</strong> defeat enemies to gain spirit and spend it according to your situation.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530280/extras/F7.gif?t=1728937720\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You must adapt and think:</strong> you use the same resource to heal and replenish ammo. To earn it you must fight, not hide.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530280/extras/F8.gif?t=1728937720\" /></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530280/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728937720","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530280/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1728937720","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530280/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728937720","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530280/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728937720","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid"